{"tid":2228781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"左報狙擊 Lunch哥：唔影響抗爭","createTime":"2020-10-03T23:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T17:30:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfc5f0dc87141056558d56d7827ee212d1eafdc","tid":2228781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T23:59:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/LIMEYIQDSVBP5OSYREMQNALL5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FLIMEYIQDSVBP5OSYREMQNALL5Q%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=9e94100b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FLIMEYIQDSVBP5OSYREMQNALL5Q%2F&h=e56dd7be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/LIMEYIQDSVBP5OSYREMQNALL5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n左報狙擊 Lunch哥：唔影響抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vR-Sj1REHfdl8jpTCNE6dgl_vyw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BBT4JRJAOFEONPOKGGRPF2QCFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvR-Sj1REHfdl8jpTCNE6dgl_vyw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBBT4JRJAOFEONPOKGGRPF2QCFU.jpg&h=8098419e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「Lunch哥」昨在商場讀報期間，有市民與他一同舉起「五一」手勢。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「Lunch哥」李國永（David）昨日又出動，在多個地區「和你Lunch」。有中共喉舌傳媒翻舊賬，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾發不雅照 自認「戇X」<br />\n<br />\n下午2時半，「Lunch哥」抵達太古城中心，在商場中庭坐下閱讀《蘋果日報》。商場多名保安隨即上前，一度要求他停止活動，他反問保安「𠵱家睇《蘋果日報》係唔係犯法？」其後他繼續活動，有數人響應在商場不同樓層閱讀《蘋果日報》，多名保安駐守，有保安曾要求改變坐姿，以免阻礙途人。<br />\n<br />\n活動期間，有一名年輕男子到場，指罵David不尊重其他抗爭者、在fb專頁刪除異見留言、性騷擾女抗爭者等，David未有正面回應。他事後接受傳媒訪問，批評對方所言的並非事實，「喺fb我都唔會亂咁講嘢，網上世界你又唔知對方係邊個，可能係警察甚至國安。」<br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》昨報道，指稱David在網上發放不雅照片。David直認不諱，表示曾指於2017至19年使用一個交友軟件，「呢件事係雙方同意先做嘅，其實冇人知我係邊個嚟嘅本身，但我就儍吓儍吓，貼咗自己大頭相，𠵱家多人識咗就俾人摷返出嚟。」David解釋有關相片只是由網上下載，並非其「鳥照」，「如果真係我嘅話，我就唔可以好似𠵱家咁冷靜，可能已經上咗天台喇，抑鬱㗎喇。」他形容自己很「戇X」，現在會避忌，他說未來會繼續抗爭，「呢啲私事唔會影響抗爭。」"},{"pid":"76859304b0dae8650b6b2194aa82398117259c99","tid":2228781,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T01:35:41.000Z","msg":"2020/1001/<br />\n阿叻攞銅紫驚章/<br />\n美總統辯論俾強國抽水/<br />\nLunch哥<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Aa2p3ri1Jk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Aa2p3ri1Jk&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=fb16cf8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Aa2p3ri1Jk</a><br />\n<br />\n42:05 講 lunch哥"},{"pid":"39c6db93ef7d6a3b654a470dc2152c7f6735899c","tid":2228781,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9756f3cc512fedb29efca8f445722b22835c35ce","tid":2228781,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"814c370ca1b5e3c231c390c71a1196092969a64e","tid":2228781,"uid":80162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"大家繼續幫對家撥火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e759419bc9cc8ad173392cf145f5f21f11ad5b2","tid":2228781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcffc8e05329d33a7c1f6546fe6ff5e0b037f521","tid":2228781,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0352cc5055dec06c222b4943295faf862b3626a1","tid":2228781,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"165f18d5bd11e024422b38e05c60cc95c959c30d","tid":2228781,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"唔怪得出面咁多屌d